<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="7Dec1931"><font color="red">7 December 1931</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I went out with Colum to see a film <i>L&apos;Afrique vous parle</i>. I think I have done a good job for Lucia. She has made initial letters for P.P. on large sheets and I wrote the text </div>
